entries.journal_entry_description: Ind knows that Kavas is trying to set him up for a fall with Valarian. Ind is going to preempt Kavas by exposing Kavas' dirty laundry first.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Null node to hang the tasks off
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Ind thinks Kavas is using a street gang as a front to hi-jack shipments. The gang is small time, and independent. Ind thinks you can bribe and fast talk your way to find out about the relationship between Kavas and the gang.  One member of this gang is a kid named Larit. See what you can find out from him.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Larit wants to have the gang to get "colors". He has asked you to make him 5 shirts.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You have finished the shirts. Talk with Larit.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Ind thinks Kavas is using a street gang as a front to hi-jack shipments. The gang is small time, and independent. Ind thinks you can bribe and fast talk your way to find out about the relationship between Kavas and the gang.  One member of this gang is a kid named Moa. See what you can find out from him.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Moa has to get some untracable CDEF pistols for an upcoming job. He wants you to craft 5 for him.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: The weapons are complete. Talk to Moa.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Waiting for Moa, and Larit to be birbed
entries.task08_comm_message_text: Well the boys speak highly of you. Come on over and we can see if you really can measure up.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: K'Cur has contacted you to arrange a meeting
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Looks like Moa and Larit put in a good word for you with the boss, K'Cur. He wants a meeting with you.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: K' Cur wants you to prove yourself to him before he trusts you. He wants you to show you aren't afraid of authority so he wants you to take out some Dewbacks used as Stormtrooper mounts.Backs that are being used by the Imperial garrison near by.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: The Dewbacks weren't a problem. Time to pump K' Cur for information.
